It's something we tried on my regular server (Vaz) &amp; it seemed quite successful., somebody had an idea..a quest.. &amp; off we went..letting the fates guide us.<br>
<br>
Thats right..a regular group exploring, fighting dying, laughing, questing all together.<br>
<br>
Obviously we can thrash out a night that suits most &amp; should roleplay problems cause some sort of dilemna..well..we can sort those should it arise.<br>
<br>
Initially, maybe a night of meeting in a Tavern someplace getting to know one anothers faults..quirks..mannersims..hell, it'll be just like table top roleplay....<br>
<br>
I propose getting together once per week at say....19:00 GMT (Plenty of time to get set).<br>
Though I am open to suggestions as I can change my play night/s to suit.<br>
<br>
